dc_title_s: Non-Public School Program Locations, SY2006/07 - 2008/09: Minnesota
dc_description_s: This file is a geodatabase that includes nonpublic school program locations, one file for each school year 2006/07  through 2008/09. Each file in this group was developed from annual information and is now provided as historical informationThese nonpublic school program locations cover nonpublic school programs with an MDE-FNS Unit Classification of 31-35. There are nonpublic schools in and outside of the MDE program that are not covered in this database. Locations have not gone through an extensive QA/QC process. This metadata is provided as a summary. The download includes seperate metadata files for each year included.
